author: exploreaswego
description: Thanks for sharing this! We are DN in Bali now, and most of everything mentioned in the video is exactly what we are going through right now. Another issue that is mentioning for short term DN like us, Visa is a major problem too during this pandemic. For 4 months, the Indonesian government was nice enough to grant us emergency stay permits, but just last week, they announced that we had to GTFO in 30 days, regardless of the situation happening at our home in the US, and the risk of flying when flights are constantly cancelled and having to go through multiple layovers in order to get home.
title: Thanks for sharing this! We are DN in Bali now, and most of everything mentioned in the video is exactly what we are going through right now. Another issue that is mentioning for short term DN like us, Visa is a major problem too during this pandemic. For 4 months, the Indonesian government was nice enough to grant us emergency stay permits, but just last week, they announced that we had to GTFO in 30 days, regardless of the situation happening at our home in the US, and the risk of flying when flights are constantly cancelled and having to go through multiple layovers in order to get home.
